---
// BGP Our Values Section
// Three core values: Believe, Connect, Grow
---

<section id="our-values" class="values-section py-20 px-[5%] bg-white">
  <div class="container max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <h2 class="section-title font-['Poppins'] text-4xl text-[#212121] font-bold text-center mb-2.5">
      Our Values
    </h2>

    <!-- Teal Underline -->
    <div class="underline w-20 h-[3px] bg-[#009688] mx-auto mb-[60px]"></div>

    <!-- Values Grid -->
    <div class="values-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Value Card 1: Believe -->
      <div class="value-card h-full bg-white rounded-lg text-center shadow-[0_5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] border border-[#f0f0f0] transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="card-inner p-10 h-full flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-['Poppins'] text-[28px] text-[#212121] mb-4">
            Believe.
          </h3>
          <div class="title-underline w-[50px] h-0.5 bg-[#9c8040] mx-auto mb-5"></div>
          <p class="text-[#424242] leading-[1.7] text-base flex-grow">
            We believe in the transformative power of faith and the limitless possibilities that come through Christ. Guided by Matthew 19:26, "With God all things are possible," we inspire hope and confidence in His plan.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Value Card 2: Connect -->
      <div class="value-card h-full bg-white rounded-lg text-center shadow-[0_5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] border border-[#f0f0f0] transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="card-inner p-10 h-full flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-['Poppins'] text-[28px] text-[#212121] mb-4">
            Connect.
          </h3>
          <div class="title-underline w-[50px] h-0.5 bg-[#9c8040] mx-auto mb-5"></div>
          <p class="text-[#424242] leading-[1.7] text-base flex-grow">
            We are dedicated to fostering meaningful connectionsâ€”between individuals, families, and with God. Through fellowship, worship, and shared experiences, we create a space where everyone feels welcomed and valued.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Value Card 3: Grow -->
      <div class="value-card h-full bg-white rounded-lg text-center shadow-[0_5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] border border-[#f0f0f0] transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="card-inner p-10 h-full flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-['Poppins'] text-[28px] text-[#212121] mb-4">
            Grow.
          </h3>
          <div class="title-underline w-[50px] h-0.5 bg-[#9c8040] mx-auto mb-5"></div>
          <p class="text-[#424242] leading-[1.7] text-base flex-grow">
            BGP is a place of spiritual and personal growth where transformation is nurtured. Together, we grow in faith, love, and purpose, becoming a light that uplifts our community and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Tablet adjustments */
  @media screen and (max-width: 992px) {
    .card-inner {
      padding: 35px 25px;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile adjustments */
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .value-card {
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .value-card p {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .values-section {
      padding: 60px 5%;
    }
  }
</style>
